{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_15053.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102901,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":103001,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102901,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"Princess went around carefully persuading each@Feather...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":103001,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Hagumu","textRight":"That even happened right here."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_15053.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":770400,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":770400,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"bgm":"bgm23_magus04","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102801,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"Wait a minute! Just listen to me for a little bit,@please!"},{"chara":[{"id":770400,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102801,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"...Phew~! You finally stopped~"},{"chara":[{"id":770400,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"...Um...I already..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp3.json","id":102801,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"I've reconsidered!"},{"chara":[{"id":770400,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"...Huh?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"id":102801,"motion":200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"This cutie will quit the whole hardcore and rigid@Magical Girl Supremacy thing!"},{"chara":[{"id":770400,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"W-what does that mean...?"},{"chara":[{"id":102801,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"No more \"Kill everyone except us!\"@I don't want to be a part of that anymore!"},{"chara":[{"id":102801}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"From now on, this cutie is going to be a softer and@milder version of herself!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102801,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"I won't waver from the idea that \"Magical Girls@are inherently superior to humans!\""},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102801,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"But you know, instead of using brute force,@from now on, I'll do it steadily and diligently."},{"chara":[{"id":102801}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"Writing letters to newspapers,@putting up flyers around town..."},{"chara":[{"id":770400,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"That's a very analog way of doing things..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102801,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"For now, that's about as far as I'm willing to go!"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":102801}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"And, we'll cooperate with the other groups, but..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp3.json","id":102801,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"If they choose the wrong path for even a second,@we'll part ways with them!"},{"chara":[{"id":102801}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"The Neo-Magius is the Neo-Magius, end of story!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102801,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"I'm going to reassess my footing and rise up with a@bang~!"},{"chara":[{"id":102801}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"Why don't you stop trying to run off,@and give me one more chance?"},{"chara":[{"id":102801,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"...How about it?"},{"chara":[{"id":770400,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"","textRight":"I don't know what to say..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_060.exp3.json","id":102801,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Himena","textLeft":"Well, let's do something about that~!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_15053.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":103001,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"bgm":"bgm23_magus02","chara":[{"id":103001,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"...That's how it went.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"lipSynch":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"(Persuasion... I guess...?)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102901,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"Seeing her like that, we couldn't help but...@you know..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":103001,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Hagumu","textRight":"Yeah."},{"chara":[{"id":103001}],"nameRight":"Hagumu","textRight":"We started working with Himena to persuade@people too."},{"chara":[{"id":102901,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"Not just us, but also the Instructor and Miyuri..."},{"chara":[{"id":103001,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Hagumu","textRight":"Even Mitsune and Sasha..."},{"chara":[{"id":102901,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"We all worked together, and as a result, we were@able to stop our faction from disbanding."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":100,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Amazing...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":103001,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"...But..."},{"chara":[{"id":103001}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"I think that Himena may be plotting a bit..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"...Huh?"},{"chara":[{"id":103001,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"Basically, she wants to make@use of whatever she can..."},{"chara":[{"id":103001}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"Both the Automatic Purification System,@and the Neo-Magius..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102901,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"So, that's why she can't just let our group fall apart."},{"chara":[{"id":102901}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"That's what our pragmatic Princess would think."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"And, that's why she was moving around so@enthusiastically...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":103001,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"Well, this is all just the Instructor's guess."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102901,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"But, it's not surprising that she'd come to that@conclusion."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Oh, I see..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102901,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Shigure","textLeft":"...But, isn't it that attitude@that makes her our Princess?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":103001,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Hagumu","textLeft":"That's right."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"Ha, haha..."},{"bg":"bg_adv_15053.jpg","nameNarration":"Kagome","narration":"After this,@I asked the two of them about their thoughts@on the future of the Neo-Magius.","narrationBg":"bg_adv_15053.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"I realized that for these girls,@the Neo-Magius is a source of comfort."},{"narration":"Then, right after I finished@my interview with the Neo-Magius..."},{"narration":"A message arrived."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
